{"tid":562054,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"a0毒撚叫春，不喜勿入，純粹發洩","createTime":"2018-02-15T14:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T16:40:54.000Z","uid":67188,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9970fefb54b68abb9bba596680ef29cf49c692cb","tid":562054,"uid":67188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"斷斷續續都叫追咗你兩年，雖然比你拒絕過，但唔知點解，我都係冇辨法死心，可能我真係太中意你。於是，我決定今次係我最後一次去追你。我同過自己講，今次追唔到就算啦，冇謂繼續浪費時間係你身上，不如去追第二個仲好。身邊ge朋友都同我講，一個女仔對你冇feel就係冇feel,冇論你做咗幾多野都好。我開頭唔信，我好天真咁以為我可以打動你，但原來，有d野真係唔係話努力去做就有回報。所以，我係你最後個次拒絕我個一刻決定咗，我唔會再去主動搵你，我唔會再有「我地有機會係埋一齊」呢個諗法，即使我都仲係咁中意你<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"b9e0ccc53e3c5827a5b2249373e0bbc0793b7780","tid":562054,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n情況差不多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4fbd673015356efd53cada33832ea1e1e5fd3c","tid":562054,"uid":13374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"依D係痴線唔係痴情<br />\n有D野留係心就夠架喇 唔好煩到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753b6babb71e4708abcbe649041a5438aecc9a8f","tid":562054,"uid":67188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9e0ccc53e3c5827a5b2249373e0bbc0793b7780","tid":562054,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n情況差不多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"明明年三十晚應該高高興興，但而家真係開心唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75669ba87df4b214f29fdf4dd8a6623fad6d68db","tid":562054,"uid":67188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4fbd673015356efd53cada33832ea1e1e5fd3c","tid":562054,"uid":13374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"依D係痴線唔係痴情<br />\n有D野留係心就夠架喇 唔好煩到人<img src=\"/assets/fa